title: Ron Paul: “Liberty is a Very Young Issue”
text:

Ron Paul: “Liberty is a Very Young Issue”
In this video, Vin Armani speaks with former Congressman Dr. Ron Paul about the momentum of the liberty movement. Paul says people feel a natural instinct to liberty but that it is “such a young issue” in the human experience.
“This experiment with self-reliance and individual liberty is something brand new. And I think it’s something with a fertile field inspite of what we’re dealing with in Washington (DC),” Paul added.
Watch Ron Paul at http://RonPaulLibertyReport.com
